title: Jefferson National Expansion Memorial: Do Business With Us
body: Explore This Park    Get Involved     Do Business With Us            Do Business With Us       The National Park Service is acquiring goods and services electronically using the Internet. All Federal Government Procurement Opportunities over $25,000 are posted on a centrally located electronic web-board called FedBizOpps (short for Federal Business Opportunities). Click here to learn more about NPS Contracts and Contracting Information.
